	,"x4freetext":[" The facility provides quasimonochromatic photon"
		,"beams from laser-Compton backscattering (LCB) in the"
		,"MeV range. The machine was operated in a new"
		,"high-resolution mode. It reduces the spectral"
		,"bandwidth of the photon beam to about 1.8% by"
		,"optimizing the electron beam parameters and using"
		,"narrower apertures for the Compton-scattering"
		,"geometry at the expense of photon-flux intensity."]
	}
